short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: BDBFind provides links to data and downloads when you view an article or patent for which BindingDB has data.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Identifies web-pages showing scientific articles for which the NIH-funded database BindingDB (bindingdb.org) can provided curated data, and provides hyperlinks to view or download these data.
